snippet.title: Quell - The brain-bending puzzle game!
snippet.description:
Quell is delightfully easy to pick up, but fiendishly brain-bending to master. Be prepared to lose yourself in this entrancing zen classic!

We've now set up a newsletter for fans of this game. If you subscribe to it, you will among the FIRST to hear about our newest projects! We'll also be running promos and competitions for subscribers.

Sign up from our Facebook page, or from www.fallentreegames.com!

http://www.fallentreegames.com

Quell is available to purchase from the App Store. Click here: 
http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/quell/id383027157?mt=8

Or, from Google Play. Click here: 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fallentreegames.quell
